OL,3,CRoad to reopen after major road work
OL,4,Cto fire-damaged mountain completed
OL,6,FA key link road that was shut for four
OL,7,Fmonths to repair damage caused by a
OL,8,Ffire is to re-open on Friday evening.
OL,10,FIn order to safely rectify hillside
OL,11,Fdamage previously caused by a major
OL,12,Ffire, the mountain road between
OL,13,FTreherbert and Rhigos was closed from
OL,14,F22 July this year.
OL,16,FThere has been a rockfall risk since a
OL,17,F2022 grass fire damaged the protective
OL,18,Fnetting on the slopes of the 491m
OL,19,F(1,610ft) Rhigos mountain.
