OL,3,CRoad to reopen after major road work
OL,4,Cto fire-damaged mountain completed
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Rhondda Cynon Taf
OL,7,FCouncil said that, over the summer,
OL,8,Fthe contractor's workforce "has made
OL,9,Fconsiderable efforts" in the repair
OL,10,Fwork.
OL,12,F"The completed scheme will rectify
OL,13,Fdamage caused by the previous fire,
OL,14,Fand ensure this commuter route between
OL,15,FTreherbert and Rhigos remains
OL,16,Favailable for communities into the
OL,17,Ffuture," they said.
